      "text": [
        "٢٨٣. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): جَاهِلُكُمْ مُزْدَادٌ وَعَالِمُكُمْ مُسَوِّفٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "283. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: The ignorant among you get too much while the learned are just put off."
